symbols/kappa.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/eta.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/sigma.gif">, the difference  will be felt if we substitute the common words, <img src="/media/symbols/nu.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/upsilon.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/nu.gif"> &nbsp; <img src="/media/symbols/delta.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/epsilon.gif"> &nbsp;  <img src="/media/symbols/mugt.gif"> &nbsp; <img src="/media/symbols/epsilon.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/omega.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/nu.gif"> &nbsp; <img src="/media/symbols/mugt.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/iota.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/kappa.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/rho.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/omicron.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/sigma.gif"> &nbsp; <img src="/media/symbols/tau.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/epsilon.gif"> &nbsp;  <img src="/media/symbols/kappa.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/alpha.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/iota.gif"> &nbsp; <img src="/media/symbols/alpha.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/rho.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/theta.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/epsilon.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/nu.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/iota.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/kappa.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/omicron.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/sigma.gif"> &nbsp;  <img src="/media/symbols/kappa.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/alpha.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/iota.gif"> &nbsp; <img src="/media/symbols/alpha.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/epsilon.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/iota.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/delta.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/gamma.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/sigma.gif">.  Or, if for the line, <img src="/media/symbols/delta.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/iota.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/phi.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/rho.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/omicron.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/nu.gif"> &nbsp; <img src="/media/symbols/alpha.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/epsilon.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/iota.gif"><img src="/media/symbols/kappa.gif"><img src="/media/symbols